# API-Football (api-sports.io) — powers the live per-match statistics
# (possession, shots, xG, etc.) shown via the 📊 button on played fixtures.
#
# 1. Create a free account at https://www.api-football.com (100 requests/day).
# 2. Copy your key from the dashboard.
# 3. Save it below in a file named `.env.local` (NOT committed).
#
# IMPORTANT: server-only secret — do NOT prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC_ (that would
# inline it into the browser bundle). It is read only in server code.
API_SPORTS_KEY=your-api-sports-key-here
